                Do not break any forces into components on the free-body diagram,
                but represent forces that can be broken into components
                on the side of the diagram.
            </li>
            <li class="subQuestion" data-answer = '\( \Sigma F = m g \sin \left( \theta \right) \text{  down the ramp} \)'>
                Determine the magnitude and direction of net force acting on the block
                in terms of \( \theta \), \( g \), and \( m \).
            </li>
            <li class="subQuestion" data-answer = '\( a = g \sin \left( \theta \right) \text{  down the ramp} \)'>
